1. Prerequisites
================

1.1 LDNS
--------

Client and server make use of the LDNS library from NL Net Labs.
Installation should be performed before building and is something like:

source can be downloaded from:
https://nlnetlabs.nl/projects/ldns/download/

cd ~
mkdir ldns
cd ldns
curl -o ldns.tar.gz https://nlnetlabs.nl/downloads/ldns/ldns-1.8.3.tar.gz
gzip -d ldns.tar.gz 
tar xvf ./ldns.tar 
autoreconf -fi
./configure 
sudo make install

1.2 JSON
--------
The client makes use of the Jansson JSON library for config parsing.

Source can be obtained from https://github.com/akheron/jansson

Installation should be performed before building and is something like:

cd ~
git clone https://github.com/akheron/jansson
cd jansson
autoreconf -fi

./configure
make
make check
sudo make install
Install json lib
git clone https://github.com/nlohmann/json
cd json
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/include/nlohmann
sudo cp ./single_include/nlohmann/json.hpp /usr/local/include/nlohmann

2. Make the code
================

Build the GNU build system
cd ~/homenet_hna
autoreconf -vfi

compile the code using configure and make
./configure
make
